headline: Home Depot (HD) Price Target Raised as Performance Remains Steady
summary: The Home Depot, Inc. (NYSE:HD) is included among the 13 Best March Dividend Stocks to Buy. On February 25, Telsey Advisory raised its price recommendation on The Home Depot, Inc.
